{"hcb488068g6fa9g42d1g8fb3gd82288422cfd": ["Remember our deal, now.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "b23130ab-772f-cb46-a016-a8b36ed097cc"], "he52ca5d0gcb9cg44acgbc9cgcd671d6037d7": ["Get out!", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "06b3c558-5f13-7e7f-1aff-13021340820c"], "ha6398f70g24e8g4e3cgb2a2gfe59ef7d12dc": ["*The squirrel lunges at your foot and bites it.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "91dbab86-8466-f94e-5350-85573cecff11"], "h17a25d46ge312g432bg8fccgf2f13b651d10": ["What was that for?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "af170804-7129-f82e-33ad-2920ea869312"], "ha97dbb8bg83efg4a00g8f6fg6dc70322a08e": ["Calm down - I'm a friend.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "51743ddd-af9a-7a65-9a6a-22de8f02814e"], "hb1e9da30gf0c0g4826gab0bga8655b3d0801": ["What sort of creature are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "f9d03ef8-4799-2037-5ad5-988cd6ff277c"], "hba98b847g9bceg4e57ga482g3fdca103077f": ["The sort that's in charge around here.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "3da2cb38-c219-8e8c-d7bd-a3c68ccecaf0"], "hbccca81bgd90cg4855g86f6g7daac6624b07": ["<i>Kick her.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "54cb82b9-d8bd-7aca-5a00-87e042adce94"], "h2cfcdd25g13ebg49aegb15cg7f33b8e39583": ["*The squirrel moves too quickly - your foot finds only air.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "af30fbf4-8f7c-5292-093d-32647bb753c1"], "h3653753eg487eg471cga0d5g67b342bab8a5": ["Try it again. I dare you.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "2fd9acef-57e1-860e-eddd-6bd6069a3c22"], "h8f25277eg5fe9g48b7g9ffeg4d0ab508390a": ["What's your problem?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "3428229b-0426-4b19-bc78-ffe13065ae7d"], "hdf646fd4g072dg4d1bg8ce5gd6f1db9a244e": ["You're trespassing. This is <i>my</i> territory.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "56e63f43-223d-bf63-d8f7-ba058fce6697"], "h35063cadg2a53g49e6g8c07gd714d3f3f78c": ["Let's start over. Friends?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "cf2dd364-2909-29a7-ad8e-c4d39c378463"], "he4cd13d0ga65bg459dg8882g52b098cf55df": ["You barged in without an invitation. I wouldn't call that friendly.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "b3c5c43f-29b5-25ba-5431-791f471d9d30"], "h9ea4cd97g2eeeg4153g91aagbdfdce22ae1d": ["See, you're in <i>my</i> territory. And I want you gone.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "cbcde8d3-b491-9c22-4902-829f36593eb9"], "h3a8a1de0ga67fg40a2ga884gf36031f5f775": ["All right, you win. I'm leaving.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "b0343387-ca2c-980d-03fa-e0a20f3402d3"], "h08f14be3g3320g4751g8a48g7cf6f0ad2d89": ["I better not catch you around here again.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "4f99d5ab-684c-05f3-b55c-5e0ef7318af3"], "h6e7f2f85g6cbag4614g9c71gc67b973d64a7": ["I'm not to be trifled with, creature.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "f589feb7-aae5-77e5-b475-7a2ad3cb7d75"], "hed4ebe9cg8a50g48fdg9734g0a72c3cecb47": ["Back off, squirrel. Or I'll make you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "f589feb7-aae5-77e5-b475-7a2ad3cb7d75"], "h85d408f3g5fa5g461egb803g1eec0b6d9ef1": ["Okay, okay, calm down. We can make a deal.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "1947c8cb-6449-462b-a6cc-70d0b16fd297"], "h9e0cfc00g0ccag4ac4ga435g39040234f7b1": ["How about this - you can stay if you keep those ugly feet on the ground.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "91e5a078-1ddd-cf3d-7636-5b1c75c45b70"], "h847d76e4ga230g44fcg86b0gc55432d6e36d": ["I'll even sweeten the pot. Here. Found this weird smelling stuff on the ground. You can keep it. But...", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "6b265dde-683e-dfdc-dfc5-b5311a0f9967"], "h254cb500gfe24g4c32gab26g9fca6e7a3f75": ["The trees are mine. Follow the rules, and I won't have to <i>intervene. </i>Got it?", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "b00f07a6-fb3d-2097-fdeb-ad287d1e07e6"], "h10f54407g6da8g454ega890g13f72311712a": ["You don't scare me. I got bears on my side.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "9ca00378-135c-3e4f-33a5-3a0c316def67"], "h26f43f69gc223g48b4gb121gef983fc84614": ["There's plenty of room for both of us.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "a1f9b254-e476-8d22-f686-cc470bddf4a9"], "ha5bca4a7g127dg46c7gaadfga4290a933a38": ["No, there's plenty of room for <i>me</i>.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "aa6fbded-2806-8c7b-2ace-8eb12fd3e05e"], "h6c1b0452g98fbg4b99g9fd6g96346b75a725": ["I could throw you halfway across Toril if I wanted to.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "1372f15b-6810-3e1e-1806-a9b12229c705"], "h9570581ag5fb0g4452g97dcgf9b254d0c1c2": ["You'd have to catch me first. Can't say I'm worried.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "e45b95cc-f1a2-6a84-7d31-2dbbb7f17c2b"], "hb4bbb8dbgca22g48b4g8292g6bdbd6610d75": ["One word and I could fry you to a crisp.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "b33c9bb6-6596-ee46-5f7e-8bee512e6717"], "h1a2d065fg5350g4645gac81g181805f074b6": ["I doubt you could muster more than a bit of smoke.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "032593ff-86d5-35b9-0dda-2a7585aae586"], "h8a748c5egcc16g444bgae38g77d102a93c9d": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "aa91d750-bfbb-ac36-4793-efaf59835e92"], "hb97620e9g2daag4671g9e43gcd137e42c230": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "66d577cc-5f93-1e80-9dd5-5a6d64debc68"], "h8e26474cga0a7g49fcg8e14g09004cae393f": ["What did I tell you? Clear out!", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "54535623-e0b1-8067-60be-16e078229a5f"], "h1aeb7d1bg1653g4103gb4f6gc347f2658d05": ["*The squirrel's tail twitches in a lukewarm salute.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "f918c494-03e1-8b93-841d-58a365899229"], "h7cb2d8ccg67c9g4a19g80d1g8d2e520e051c": ["*The squirrel flicks her tail at you and turns away.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "27e3ea7b-db6f-c938-5f02-3894adc8920d"], "h3752a0a1g3154g4978gae9egeb5e7bdf23f4": ["*Cht!*", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "584df300-7984-4528-2651-7146a3df8d83"], "ha2421de8g2fb1g4c42gb3degb8a3d51e4d6c": ["*Cht cht!*", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "4d2a8eb1-5212-63eb-7dde-d48f7a5e6d5f"], "hffd1cd5agab96g4c6dga27bge25c6046028a": ["<i>Kick the squirrel.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "5a2a522d-05c8-cb49-662f-74dbc36343ad"], "h4c9d6ab1g24d2g4cacg8bd6gc738a4076825": ["<i>Study the creature's behaviour.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "122e1553-b649-56b0-b5bd-facafbda6474"], "h82443c36g9948g4f70gb8e3gd0859cc3e575": ["*You follow the squirrel's gaze to a pair of clumsy, ugly feet. Your own, on <i>her</i> territory.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "42d68a10-2579-885b-dcad-2080a5d5f4e0"], "ha9fcbe67ga540g4aadg925fg1d0e9f503cf3": ["*Looking around, 'her territory' extends from one end of the grove to another.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "132775fb-8891-ba3a-3470-19bbe859f7f3"], "h686ef77eg0245g45cfgb150ga33704fd344a": ["What is this bizarre creature?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "2f1aa33a-0bac-880a-4547-da7ddfcfb712"], "hbc8576bfg70cdg418ag8d39gff59b234e1ab": ["*It is unnecessarily odd. A small, noisy pest with a bushy tail.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "6206a7b5-b70b-3429-3474-7668be04bb84"], "h0955f698g366eg41d2ga8a1g3b460fc86a0d": ["*You cannot imagine what purpose such a creature could possibly serve.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "b7ed999d-581a-9533-62fe-c76c8d03cd6b"], "h5c58141ag52fbg4599gb6d7g192c1cfed0a8": ["<i>Kick her.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "88afdfc0-0941-9f34-bf72-2769bac8c7e8"], "hb116b65dg5790g4617gabebg00eb63798723": ["*The squirrel chitters scornfully as your foot whistles over her head.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "a75050be-202f-ba39-d54b-9ef694d40bf5"], "hb3fe268fg78edg40a7g9b7cg23534c96fa5d": ["<i>Reach for your weapon.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "35f84d25-b9ce-b5fa-7b3e-a6ebefeef51b"], "hfbf83619ga446g425bg9e14gcfe92f640b3b": ["*The squirrel flees, shrieking with indignant terror.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "000f90ac-570c-65d4-41e7-33cdee5cb0b2"], "h6c7f828ag2f61g4df4gb8fcgfa77d41392dc": ["*With a shriek, the squirrel flees.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "97c74391-e5cc-4cfc-e07c-1802e8149aa6"], "he86f7b87gbc74g411fg878fgcdb72c845f3b": ["<i>Try to kick her again.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "dc07a2ee-d960-0b75-1663-dc33470e480a"], "hcaf14eaag373bg4581gbdd4gf7be7ac4017f": ["There is no shame in defending against tiny wild beasts.", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "1137fde0-5d67-e6d1-bde5-6d6909350d70"], "h20c25c0dg6771g47d8gbd7cg67a3718da392": ["_", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "007ae71f-080d-83a1-926c-a9c16a66bd38"], "h6b6e0ed8g7a34g408dgbe80g7ef7991b23d4": ["*You claim victory over the squirrel, though you're not sure why you were fighting to begin with.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "9776f751-b5bf-f821-d159-8bce7839ace3"], "h17dac5c9g6e3dg481cgbbb0g6378c99d0dfd": ["*It seems you've claimed the squirrel's territory by right of conquest.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "f33242a5-f50a-e58b-9268-81f2b3ec76ab"], "h9f6af5f4g39cbg44c6gaa13g959e4e0fed28": ["No! What did you do?!", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "f22801ef-6d3f-9014-6321-9e267d2ebf38"], "h64917135g8220g49d4g8a1cg67249a1f25bc": ["Oh it's everywhere. You ruined a perfectly good snack.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "39bcdb3f-4822-e28c-2653-d7f0ba4fc910"], "he520f456gf530g4216gb5dcg12f6c25d6887": ["*This also misses.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "de173ff4-77fb-d4ae-2208-5328673c6ab9"], "h6fee03ebg8e9dg472bg9f6fg963dd6ba6728": ["Not even close. To think I took you for a threat.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "ed9cf49a-6df7-abc3-e4f3-56aa042e377c"], "h5809850fg9da8g4832gb237ga058f9998fa1": ["Now get moving. I'm tired of looking at you.", "35ed8eab-1e0b-4ec8-92f2-1b8510cb3ad8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "6158a58e-bdf2-b801-8f52-f7ec1792c442"], "hfa562e28g2d48g4c42gb07cg78048fe22173": ["*The squirrel bounds away, chittering wildly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "f8904456-7245-eada-314d-d4fbc27da4f1"], "hf889ec6bgf3e1g4930gaca0g72b48021a56e": ["*With a cocky flick of her tail, the squirrel scampers away.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "cb77333d-aa68-690f-f0dc-46e36c140f66"], "h279737b9gc032g4ebegb476g8b8989f322a6": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "18c65592-aba2-20dd-27f2-810b3819a52e"], "h6ddda042gdecag4df8g8760g7b5ee05204a9": ["<i>Scold her with a click of your tongue.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "29497bbe-9385-0255-14ef-dd93b756e39f"], "he432e4b2gf512g414dgae66gef838640d65a": ["*She studies you for a moment before twitching her ears. Compromise.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "a4911269-e953-df5a-a12f-5d934e7901cd"], "hf39d2a78g73b3g4980g91cfgdcd491f090cd": ["*After a final squeak of warning - break the rules, and there will be trouble - she scurries away.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "3ed6ebf3-a4a1-1baf-84d0-938722d5a502"], "h4e7a83cdgdda2g483ag9906gf7b5eac266b5": ["Get out of here. Now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "bd815301-87e4-81d0-2f78-e11d83df2f1c"], "h5d87b245gd6acg4c89g9366g6e2b03fb56cc": ["*The squirrel freezes, muscles tensed in alarm. She gets the message.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "ae9f32a2-aec1-2dbe-f70b-a92eb5b65633"], "h284d4a60gfe02g422ag8a81g0848c95ae43c": ["*She chatters back, louder and at length.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "e53ff306-ba48-8513-8aa2-6b585f4213f3"], "haef55652g5dd7g4258g8d34gd9c0638e699e": ["*Tail rigid with irritation, she scampers off.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "af66ca4e-7e05-083c-1442-35b3e1e70a2a"], "hec9246deg3e97g415dg8514g17eff9a5a1f6": ["<i>Growl threateningly.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "35078f3a-85c9-7aa2-7b6b-c01c6a7912e1"], "h15f1a4d1gd66cg4f08g96abg0ea8ca23177a": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "35776221-9774-6d6b-7a10-46b4172812ae"], "he2969cc3gd824g4377gbccdg3ab67102fe16": ["*Her motivations elude you. Distracted by your thoughts, you let your guard down.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "a0790c5f-eff4-f5f9-e3a7-efef317eafc0"], "hbfa2bc08g2c40g48e0gbba7gefcb83641b12": ["*The squirrel bites your foot again.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_Squirrel.html", "d04f144e-e00e-44ea-e2ce-781a7128b991"]}